<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<%= render 'head' %>
		<meta name="description" content="Frequently Asked Questions Page">
	</head>
	<body>
		<%= render 'top-bar' %>
		<%= render 'nav-bar' %>
		<div class="container-fluid grey-background pb-3 pt-4" id="faq-page-outer-container">
			<div class="container-fluid p-0" id="faq-page-inner-container">
				<p class="responsive-text-size yellow-text">Bringing live music to you in a time of social distancing</p>
				<p class="green-text responsive-text-big">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</p>
				<p class="responsive-text-med">What's this all about?</p>
				<ul class="pl-4 pl-sm-5">
					<li class="responsive-text-size">
						The social distancing guidelines related to the COVID-19 pandemic have made it hard to find live music in the usual places. Driveway Bands is a temporary community service, bringing live music to you and your guests, on your property. Your driveway can become a performance venue.
					</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="responsive-text-med">What kind of music do you play?</p>
				<ul class="pl-4 pl-sm-5">
					<li class="responsive-text-size">
						The band doing this - Random and True - mostly covers singer/songwriters from the 70s, 80s and 90s. Please click <%= link_to("randomandtrue.com", 'https://www.randomandtrue.com/', class: "responsive-text-size", target: "_blank") %> to access video and learn more.
					</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="responsive-text-med">What does it cost?</p>
				<ul class="pl-4 pl-sm-5">
					<li class="responsive-text-size">
						Concerts cost $100 for a 60-minute set and $150 for a 90-minute set. In case budget is an issue, please contact drivewaybands@gmail.com to see if we can work something out.
					</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="responsive-text-med">Which towns do you serve?</p>
				<ul class="pl-4 pl-sm-5">
					<li class="responsive-text-size">
						Concerts are available in the following towns:
							<ul class="pb-2 pt-1">
								<li>Allenspark</li>
								<li>Drake</li>
								<li>Estes Park</li>
								<li>Glen Haven</li>
								<li>Meeker Park</li>
								<li>Pinewood Springs</li>
							</ul>
						We may be able to work something out even if your town is not listed, so please contact us at drivewaybands@gmail.com before giving up on the idea.
					</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="responsive-text-med">What do I need to provide?</p>
				<ul class="pl-4 pl-sm-5">
					<li class="responsive-text-size">
						The band will need a dry and fairly flat area about 6' x 12'. Electric power is needed to run the PA, but an unamplified concert is an option for locations with no electricity.
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>